Image::ANSI - Load, create, manipulate and save ANSI files

This module allows you to load, create and manipulate files made up of
ANSI escape codes, aka ANSI art.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


